title: Combichrist - Today we are all demons
description:
The new combichrist album, today we are all demons introduces a harsher, more in your face sound. this album is impossible to find anywhere else other than demonoid. i dont like how inclusive demonoid is so i decided to put this up for all you combichrist fans out there that didn't want to wait for it to come out.


                                   (-C-)
